name: latinaDollLikeness
description:
I was inspired by the various likeness LoRAs made by Kbr for Asian doll depiction and wanted to create one for Latinas.

Recommended weights: 0.2 - 0.6

If you like this LoRA and wish to support me, consider buying me a beer at https://www.buymeacoffee.com/WaifuWizardWong 🍺 It takes a lot of time to collect training material, train, and test. Your support will encourage me to make more LoRAs like this. I would greatly appreciate it!

Be sure to check out my other LoRAs!
